	/**
	 * Unarchives the value associated with the given key as an array.
	 *
	 * Examples:
	 * ---
	 * auto archive = new XmlArchive!();
	 * archive.beginUnarchiving(data);
	 * auto id = archive.unarchiveArray("arr", (size_t length) {
